Generic single-database configuration with async support for MySQL.

This directory contains Alembic migration scripts for the metadata management system.

## Usage

### Create a new migration
```bash
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description of changes"
```

### Apply migrations
```bash
alembic upgrade head
```

### Rollback migrations
```bash
alembic downgrade -1
```

### View migration history
```bash
alembic history
```

### View current revision
```bash
alembic current
```

## Notes

- All migrations use async SQLAlchemy with aiomysql driver
- Database charset is set to utf8mb4 with utf8mb4_unicode_ci collation
- Connection pooling is configured in app/core/database.py
